sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as Minio/S3<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant Pod as Pipeline Component Pod
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward with TLS 1.2+
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate JWT Token
    OAuth->>API: Forward (HTTP/8888)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL protocol
    DB-->>API: Confirmation
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>Argo: Notify workflow creation
    Argo->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pods<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8s-->>Pod: Start pipeline execution
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline created response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Artifact Storage During Execution

    Pod->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>S3 API, Access Key/Secret
    S3-->>Pod: Artifact stored
    Pod->>MLMD: Record artifact metadata<br/>gRPC/8080
    MLMD->>DB: Persist metadata<br/>MySQL/3306
    DB-->>MLMD: Confirmation
    MLMD-->>Pod: Metadata recorded

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Workflow Metadata Sync

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status update
    PA->>DB: Update run status<br/>MySQL/3306
    PA->>S3: Fetch workflow logs<br/>S3 API
    S3-->>PA: Log artifacts
    PA->>DB: Store log references
    DB-->>PA: Confirmation

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: Artifact Retrieval

    User->>Route: GET /artifacts/{id}<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward
    OAuth->>API: Authenticated request
    API->>S3: Generate signed URL<br/>Access Key/Secret
    S3-->>API: Signed URL (60s expiry)
    API-->>OAuth: Redirect to signed URL
    OAuth-->>Route: Redirect response
    Route-->>User: Redirect to S3
    User->>S3: Direct download<br/>Signed URL auth
    S3-->>User: Artifact data

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 5: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    participant SW as Scheduled Workflow
    SW->>DB: Check scheduled runs<br/>MySQL/3306
    DB-->>SW: Pending schedules
    SW->>API: Create pipeline run<br/>HTTP/8888, SA Token
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR
    K8s-->>Argo: Trigger workflow
